etch deeply into the soul?♪

162
00:14:44,300 --> 00:14:48,060
♪I see you, like a timid soldier,
crumbling to escape♪

163
00:14:48,060 --> 00:14:51,060
♪Let pain bury the exclusive territory
of love♪

164
00:14:51,080 --> 00:14:52,800
Why are you avoiding me?

165
00:14:53,900 --> 00:14:56,020
If you don't offer me some rewards,

166
00:14:56,980 --> 00:14:59,180
I'll have to order my army
to leave for the south now.

167
00:15:00,220 --> 00:15:03,500
Tell me, for those who keep observing
outside of the Palace,

168
00:15:04,400 --> 00:15:06,160
what will they do then?

169
00:15:06,580 --> 00:15:10,580
♪Time scattered in the sky,
falling into the crevices of memory♪

170
00:15:11,240 --> 00:15:13,100
Chu Li, go and get that brat here

171
00:15:13,100 --> 00:15:14,720
from the Palace of Xuyang.

172
00:15:15,600 --> 00:15:16,160
Yes.

173
00:15:16,160 --> 00:15:16,600
No.

174
00:15:18,620 --> 00:15:21,980
♪Embrace you between day and night♪

175
00:15:22,760 --> 00:15:24,360
His Highness is joking.

176
00:15:24,360 --> 00:15:25,600
Don't bother, General Chu.

177
00:15:25,700 --> 00:15:29,700
♪Hold you tightly, like a distant past♪

178
00:15:29,700 --> 00:15:33,980
♪Cross through the days in the wind,
entwined in the endless sea♪

179
00:15:33,980 --> 00:15:36,980
♪Even if lost♪

180
00:16:11,860 --> 00:16:19,100
♪There's a kind of powerlessness,
watching you leave♪

181
00:16:19,100 --> 00:16:24,500
♪Pretend to be indifferent,
but my heart can't breathe♪

182
00:16:24,500 --> 00:16:31,020
♪I dare not imagine our future,
what kind of relationship it will be♪

183
00:16:31,020 --> 00:16:38,020
♪Praying for time to slow down,
not to erase my memories♪

184
00:16:38,020 --> 00:16:41,380
♪From then on, I lost you♪

185
00:16:41,380 --> 00:16:44,340
♪But I still think of you,
unable to let go♪

186
00:16:44,340 --> 00:16:49,700
♪You always appear
in every dream of mine♪

187
00:16:49,700 --> 00:16:52,220
♪Coming close and then going away.
I can't love you anymore♪

188
00:16:52,220 --> 00:16:55,660
♪From now on,
I am the only person to stay♪

189
00:16:55,660 --> 00:16:59,340
♪Dare not disturb.
I can only hold tightly onto memories♪

190
00:16:59,340 --> 00:17:01,860
♪How can I leave someone I've loved?♪

191
00:17:01,860 --> 00:17:05,020
♪It's impossible to return to before♪

192
00:17:05,980 --> 00:17:12,780
♪Tell me, how do we settle our regrets?♪

193
00:17:12,780 --> 00:17:18,780
♪Because I loved you too much,
I let go of my pride♪

194
00:17:19,420 --> 00:17:25,100
♪I can't learn to leave you so easily♪

195
00:17:25,100 --> 00:17:28,380
♪You left with just a goodbye♪

196
00:17:28,380 --> 00:17:33,740
♪Letting me linger in the same spot,
heartache for years♪

197
